title: Cannot sync a .java file and another resource
OB: When attempting to sync a .java file and another resource, the synchronization process fails.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the software. 
2. Navigate to the synchronization settings. 
3. Select a .java file and another resource to sync. 
4. Initiate the synchronization process.
5. Observe the failure of the synchronization process.
